[~tanu.ajmera] Thanks for the patch. The patch looks good. One minor issue which is not related to this patch.

1. The below null check is not required 

{code}
 bindExternalClasses();
 if (rm != null)
{code}

rm gets accessed even before the null check from bindExternalClasses, so no use having the null check.

{code}
  private void bindExternalClasses() {
    YarnConfiguration yarnConf = new YarnConfiguration(rm.getConfig());
{code}

